Package: autoresearch
Title: Autonomous Optimization Framework for R Programs, Scripts and Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("AutoResearch", "Team", email = "autoresearch@example.com",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A flexible optimization framework that can automatically tune and
    improve any R program, script, or statistical model. Supports hyperparameter
    optimization via Grid Search, Random Search, and Bayesian Optimization
    (Gaussian Process surrogate with Expected Improvement). An intelligent
    Research Agent adaptively narrows the search space over multiple rounds,
    combining exploration and exploitation. Tracks all experiments with
    reproducible results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
